<subSubSection id="73FB72F0CE5812593D44F9DFFD8BFAFC" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="7" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" type="description">
<paragraph id="3B5E217BCE58125B3D44F9DFFE66F9EC" blockId="4.[264,980,1524,1585]" box="[264,392,1559,1585]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
(
<figureCitation id="A3DA3DFECE58125B3D5DF9DFFE91F9EC" box="[273,383,1559,1585]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–4" captionStartId="5.[264,383,1579,1603]" captionTargetBox="[284,1303,448,1539]" captionTargetId="figure-122@5.[267,1327,422,1581]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 1–4. Chrysotimus acutatus sp. nov. (male). 1. Wing; 2. first flagellomere, lateral view; 3. genitalia, ventral view; 4. genitalia, lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5048634" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5048634/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Figs. 1–4</figureCitation>
)
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3B5E217BCE58125B3D44F9AFFB29F974" blockId="4.[264,1323,1639,1905]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Diagnosis. Palpus blackish. Hind tarsomere 1 with 6 sparse short black ventral bristles on basal 1/4 and row of 5–6 pv. Hypandrium enlarged with indistinct apical incision.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3B5E217BCE58125B3D74F97FFBC9F90C" blockId="4.[264,1323,1639,1905]" box="[312,1063,1718,1745]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Description. 
<emphasis id="0995FD69CE58125B3D83F97EFDFBF90D" bold="true" box="[463,533,1718,1744]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Male.</emphasis>
Body length: 
<quantity id="FC198C9ECE58125B3EF0F97FFCC6F90C" box="[700,808,1719,1745]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.15" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" unit="mm" value="2.15">2.15 mm</quantity>
, wing length 
<quantity id="FC198C9ECE58125B3F8AF97FFBCCF90C" box="[966,1058,1719,1745]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.2" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" unit="mm" value="2.2">2.2 mm</quantity>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3B5E217BCE58125A3D74F917FB44FE83" blockId="4.[264,1323,1639,1905]" lastBlockId="5.[264,1323,284,350]" lastPageId="5" lastPageNumber="6" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Head metallic green with pale gray pollen; frons and face brilliant. Hairs and bristles on head yellow. Ocellar tubercle weak, with 2 very long oc and 2 very short posterior hairs. Lower postocular bristles (including ventral hairs) pale. Antenna (
<figureCitation id="A3DA3DFECE58125B382BF8E7FB41F894" box="[1127,1199,1839,1865]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–4" captionStartId="5.[264,383,1579,1603]" captionTargetBox="[284,1303,448,1539]" captionTargetId="figure-122@5.[267,1327,422,1581]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 1–4. Chrysotimus acutatus sp. nov. (male). 1. Wing; 2. first flagellomere, lateral view; 3. genitalia, ventral view; 4. genitalia, lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5048634" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5048634/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Fig. 2</figureCitation>
) blackish; first flagellomere blackish, rather short, about 0.56 times as long as wide; arista dorsal, with basal segment very short. Proboscis brown, with brown hairs; palpus blackish, with brownish hairs and 2 brownish apical bristles and 3 brownish marginal bristles.
</paragraph>
<caption id="6F9E71F3CE59125A3D44F9E3FCCBF9B8" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5048634" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5048634" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5048634/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" startId="5.[264,383,1579,1603]" targetBox="[284,1303,448,1539]" targetPageId="5">
<paragraph id="3B5E217BCE59125A3D44F9E3FCCBF9B8" blockId="5.[264,1322,1579,1637]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">
<emphasis id="0995FD69CE59125A3D44F9E3FE5BF99E" bold="true" box="[264,437,1579,1603]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">FIGURES 1–4.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="FCE15AF8CE59125A3DF1F9E4FD4BF99E" authority="Wang &amp; Yang &amp; Grootaert, 2005" authorityName="Wang &amp; Yang &amp; Grootaert" authorityYear="2005" box="[445,677,1580,1603]" class="Insecta" family="Dolichopodidae" genus="Chrysotimus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="acutatus" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="0995FD69CE59125A3DF1F9E4FD4BF99E" box="[445,677,1580,1603]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Chrysotimus acutatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="12A64012CE59125A3EE1F9E4FCEFF99E" box="[685,769,1580,1603]" pageId="5" pageNumber="6" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
(male). 1. Wing; 2. first flagellomere, lateral view; 3. genitalia, ventral view; 4. genitalia, lateral view.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph id="3B5E217BCE5912593D74F909FC28FD93" blockId="5.[264,1322,1729,1875]" lastBlockId="6.[264,1324,284,1313]" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="7" pageId="5" pageNumber="6">Thorax metallic green with pale gray pollen, mesonotum and scutellum brilliant. Hairs and bristles on thorax yellow; 6 dc, 4–5 irregularly paired acr short and hair­like; scutellum with 2 pairs of bristles. Propleuron with 1 brownish bristle on lower portion. Legs including coxae yellow, with all tarsomere 5 brown. Hairs and bristles on legs yellow; coxae with yellowish hairs and bristles; fore coxa with 3–4 anterior and apical bristles, mid coxa with 2–3 anterior and apical bristles, hind coxa with 1 brown outer bristle near middle. Mid femur with 1 av apically; hind femur with 1 short av and 1 short pv apically. Mid tibia with 2 ad and 2 pd, apically with 4 bristles; hind tibia with 1 ad at basal 1/3, 2 pd on apical half, and apically with 3 bristles. Fore and mid tarsomere 1 each with row of 6–7 v. Hind tarsomere 1 with 6 sparse short black ventral bristles on basal 1/4 and row of 5–6 pv. Relative lengths of tibia and 5 tarsomeres of legs. LI 3.4: 2.0: 0.9: 0.6: 0.4: 0.4; LII 3.8: 2.5: 1.0: 0.7: 0.6: 0.4; LIII 5.0: 4.0: 1.3: 1.0: 0.6: 0.5.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3B5E217BCE5A12593D74FD94FDFBFD14" blockId="6.[264,1324,284,1313]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
Wing hyaline (
<figureCitation id="A3DA3DFECE5A12593DBEFD94FDD3FDAB" box="[498,573,604,630]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–4" captionStartId="5.[264,383,1579,1603]" captionTargetBox="[284,1303,448,1539]" captionTargetId="figure-122@5.[267,1327,422,1581]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 1–4. Chrysotimus acutatus sp. nov. (male). 1. Wing; 2. first flagellomere, lateral view; 3. genitalia, ventral view; 4. genitalia, lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5048634" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5048634/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
), veins brownish; R 
<subScript id="A765233ECE5A12593F73FDA0FCB0FDA4" attach="left" box="[831,862,616,633]" fontSize="7" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">4+5</subScript>
and M parallel apically, CuAx ratio (length of m­cu / length of distal portion of CuA) 0.25. Squama yellow with pale yellow hairs. Halter brownish.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3B5E217BCE5A12593D74FD1FFE23FCC4" blockId="6.[264,1324,284,1313]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Abdomen metallic green with pale gray pollen, dorsum brilliant. Hairs and bristles on abdomen brown.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3B5E217BCE5A12593D74FCEFFD41FC64" blockId="6.[264,1324,284,1313]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
Male genitalia (
<figureCitation id="A3DA3DFECE5A12593DBCFCEFFD8CFC9C" box="[496,610,807,833]" captionStart="FIGURES 1–4" captionStartId="5.[264,383,1579,1603]" captionTargetBox="[284,1303,448,1539]" captionTargetId="figure-122@5.[267,1327,422,1581]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURES 1–4. Chrysotimus acutatus sp. nov. (male). 1. Wing; 2. first flagellomere, lateral view; 3. genitalia, ventral view; 4. genitalia, lateral view." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5048634" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5048634/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Figs. 3–4</figureCitation>
). Epandrium distinctly longer than wide, apically with bifurcated lateral process; surstylus not distinctly separated from epandrium, acute apically; cercus long with round base and acute apex; hypandrium enlarged with indistinct apical incision, covering epandrium partly.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3B5E217BCE5A12593D74FC0FFDF6FC3C" blockId="6.[264,1324,284,1313]" box="[312,536,967,993]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Female. Unknown.</paragraph>
